{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2477 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2477 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2477","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"'member' : static data member cannot be initialized via derived class","pos":[618,687]},{"content":"A static data member of a template class was initialized incorrectly.","pos":[694,763]},{"content":"This is a breaking change with versions of the Visual C++ compiler prior to Visual Studio .NET 2003, in order to conform to the ISO C++ standard.","pos":[764,909]},{"content":"The following sample generates C2477:","pos":[916,953]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2477 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2477\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2477\"\nms.assetid: 60bc324b-6605-4833-8099-a291efc712e7\ncaps.latest.revision: 9\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2477\n'member' : static data member cannot be initialized via derived class  \n  \n A static data member of a template class was initialized incorrectly. This is a breaking change with versions of the Visual C++ compiler prior to Visual Studio .NET 2003, in order to conform to the ISO C++ standard.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2477:  \n  \n```  \n// C2477.cpp  \n// compile with: /Za /c  \ntemplate <class T>  \nstruct S {  \n   static int n;  \n};  \n  \nstruct X {};  \nstruct A: S<X> {};  \n  \nint A::n = 0;   // C2477  \n  \ntemplate<>  \nint S<X>::n = 0;  \n```"}